data.description: Stunning home available on a quarter acre lot in Prairieville! The spacious, open concept living, kitchen, and dining area is perfect for entertaining with a fireplace, breakfast nook, and tons of cabinet space including a large kitchen island. The primary bedroom features an en suite with a soaking tub, dual sinks, a separate shower, and large walk in closet with built in organization. The real star of the show is this yard! There is a covered patio with a large extended concrete patio, a separate storage shed, and a full fenced in yard big enough for any project. With a two car garage, crown molding, and stainless steel appliances, this home is perfectly move in ready.  **Sellers are highly motivated and ready to negotiate!**
